data.description: *Back on market due to no fault of the seller. Buyer terminated a day before closing!* Welcome Home! Top Floor 2 Level Penthouse Loft Style Home overlooking pool with private roof top terrace. Renovated kitchen with open floor plan offering tons of natural light and beautiful hardwood floors. Entertainer's island kitchen featuring serving bar, granite counters and stainless appliances. 2-story entry foyer. Balcony on *Main level * overlooks the pool. Main level bedroom features deep trey ceiling and large walk in closet. Main level bath has vaulted ceilings and tile surrounding the soaking tub/shower and linen shelving. Washer/Dryer in its own space off the bathroom. 2nd level features a private oversized owner's suite with large walk in closet and an ensuite with tile surrounding the garden soaking tub along with a separate tile shower. Off the primary bedroom is the private rooftop terrace featuring relaxing views. This condo is located in a 4-story building with an elevator and only 4 homes on each floor. Enjoy the pool and courtyards this gated boutique community has. Walk to restaurants, shopping, grocery stores and the Tara Theatre. Quick access to 75/85, 400. Within minutes to Buckhead, Midtown, Emory, CDC, Piedmont Park and everything Atlanta has to offer. Seller is open to leaving home fully furnished. Schedule your tour today!
